<br>
A business woman, making 6 digits, single, and very successful in all aspects of her life. Travels for work, which is required for her job. <br>
<br>
She is out one night, and someone rapes her. First of all, the mental anguish caused by this has already tortured her. She finds out she is pregnant. Now, having been around a pregnant woman recently, I know what they go through. This woman, would not be able to fly around the world, so now she can not complete her job. She could take maternity leave via FMLA but it has now interrupted her plans in life. During the time she is gone, someone else gets a promotion she may have been able to get. <br>
<br>
She now has the fetus of a sick, deranged individual growing inside her. What kind of fucked up genes does the father have? She now has to live with the mental anguish that she is pregnant with the man who violently and maliciously attacked her in a savage crime of lust, which she has to carry the memory of for the rest of her life. <br>
<br>
You are saying she should live with that baby growing inside her for 9 months, interrupting her life? Who are you to make that decision for her? Would you want someone telling you what you have to do with your life? Hell no. So why should they?<br>
